      "description": "Prohibits the largest landfill as of 1\/1\/2011 in a county with a population greater than or equal to 500,000 from accepting municipal solid waste, beginning 7\/1\/17. Prohibits landfills in counties with populations less than 500,000 from accepting municipal solid waste after a date determined by council resolution. (SD1)"
